<topic template="Default" status="Needs Review" modified="2026-04-29T09:27:59.064Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>NC 程序输入/输出程序</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">NC 程序输入/输出程序</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;">NC 程序数据可从 CNC-MEM 输入/输出到外置卡或 USB 闪存驱动器。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">输出程序</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">将外置卡或 USB 闪盘插入主操作面板上的 PCMCIA 端口或 USB 端口。(参照<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="SRAM-Backup" anchor="Fig3.5" target="_blank" style="color:#0000ff;">图 3.5</link>）。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">选择编辑模式。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[PROG]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[DIR]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">输入 0-9999。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[EXEC]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">开始将程序从 NC 输出到存储卡。程序传送期间，输出文本在信息显示区闪烁。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; line-height:1.50;"><image src="Figure 2.3.2 NC Program Output Procedure.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="60.00%" width="422" height="319" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><anchor id="OutputProcedure" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER2=3%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; &#160;NC 程序输出程序</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50; page-break-before:always;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">输入程序</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px;">向机床输入 NC 程序时，请按照以下步骤将外置卡或 USB 闪存盘中的文件复制到 CNC-MEM 文件夹中。</para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">将外置卡或 USB 闪盘插入主操作面板上的 PCMCIA 端口或 USB 端口。(参照<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="SRAM-Backup" anchor="Fig3.5" target="_blank" style="color:#0000ff;">图 3.5</link>）。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">选择编辑模式。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[PROG]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[DIR]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[DEVICE]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[DEVICE]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[M-CARD]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FINPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FINPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">输入文件编号并按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[F SET]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[EXEC]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">开始从存储卡输入程序。在程序传输过程中，输入文本在信息显示区闪烁。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-34px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:34px; line-height:1.50;"><image src="Figure 2.3.3 NC Program Input Procedure.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="60.00%" width="445" height="338" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><anchor id="InputProcedure" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER2=3%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; &#160;NC 程序输入步骤</text></para>
